</div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default tab-feature">
<div class="panel-heading">
<h4 class="panel-title">
<a class="accordion-toggle tab-feature-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting#collapse-wordpress-why-a2" aria-expanded="false">Why Should I Choose A2 For WordPress Hosting?</a>
</h4>
</div>
<div id="collapse-wordpress-why-a2" class="panel-collapse collapse" aria-expanded="true">
<div role="tabpanel" class="feature-content fade tab-feature-content panel-body fw-previous-tab-pane active in" id="wordpress-why-a2">
<p>Do you mean besides our screaming fast servers, easy WordPress setup, ultra-reliable service and amazing support team? How about because we can offer you <strong>the recommended WordPress setup right out of the box</strong>? Not only do you get the best versions of both PHP and&nbsp;MySQL/MariaDB, but we also include a <strong>free SSL Certificate</strong> for your site. This makes the ideal WordPress web hosting environment according WordPress themselves.</p>
<p>Our WordPress Hosting solutions are designed to be user-friendly, yet they are loaded with a number of features that developers are looking for. That means both WordPress experts and users who have never hosted a site before will both love our solutions. You can even choose which version of WordPress you want to use including WordPress v<a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/4">4</a>, <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/5">5</a>, <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/5.1">5.1</a>, <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/5.2">5.2</a>, <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/5.3">5.3</a>, <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/5.4">5.4</a>, <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/5.5">5.5</a> and <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/5.6">5.6</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default tab-feature">
<div class="panel-heading">
<h4 class="panel-title">
<a class="accordion-toggle tab-feature-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting#collapse-wordpress-a2-fast" aria-expanded="false">What Makes A2 So Fast?</a>
</h4>
</div>
<div id="collapse-wordpress-a2-fast" class="panel-collapse collapse" aria-expanded="true">
<div role="tabpanel" class="feature-content fade tab-feature-content panel-body fw-previous-tab-pane active in" id="wordpress-a2-fast">
<p>Since our launch in 2003, A2 Hosting has been on the cutting edge of hosting and development technology. We were one of the first hosts to offer technology like PHP 5 and SSDs. Ensuring our customers get the best software and hardware for their sites are just one of the reasons why we can offer the fastest WordPress Hosting. While we won't give you the whole recipe for why A2 Hosting has the fastest WordPress Hosting, here are a few key ingredients.</p>
<ul>
<li>AMD EPYC Servers w/ NVMe Drives - When you choose our Turbo Servers, your WordPress site comes hosted on these next generation servers. Just some of the advantages of our Turbo platform features these blazing fast servers:
<ul>
<li>Able to handle 9X more traffic</li>
<li>3X FASTER read speeds</li>
<li>30% FASTER CPU Performance</li>
<li>2X FASTER to first byte&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Choice Of Data Center Location - The closest your website is hosted to your visitors, the less amount of time it takes data to travel to your visitors. At A2 Hosting, you get to choose your data center location, reducing latency and increasing the performance of your WordPress websites.</li>
<li>Performance Plus Option - Your WordPress Hosting account features the Performance Plus option. When you subscribe to this service, we add additinal resources to your account so that your site is able to maintain its speed even during traffic spikes. This is a great service for websites that experience traffic surges during particular hours, days, months or seasons.</li>
<li>A2 Site Accelerator - While many hosts are unable or unwilling to offer caching solutions on a Shared Hosting account, A2 Hosting actually gives you a tool to help you setup these speed enhancing tools up with a few clicks. Found within your cPanel control panel, the A2 Site Accelerator includes:
<ul>
<li>Turbo Cache - Available on Turbo Hosting accounts. This tool stores the entire HTML contents of your website within cache and is able to serve your site without having to run PHP.</li>
<li>OPcache/APC - Tests have show that using these caching systems have cut PHP response times in half!</li>
<li>Memcached - Is able to increase your database speed by storing the most important data in memory for fast retrieval.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Need help with developing your site? Considering working with our WordPress development partner <a href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting/codeable" target="_blank">Codeable</a>. They'll even give you a free credit on your first project!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel panel-default tab-feature">
<div class="panel-heading">
<h4 class="panel-title">
<a class="accordion-toggle tab-feature-title collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="https://www.a2hosting.com/wordpress-hosting#collapse-wordpress-which-package" aria-expanded="false">Which WordPress Hosting package should I buy?</a>
</h4>
</div>
<div id="collapse-wordpress-which-package" class="panel-collapse collapse" aria-expanded="true">
<div role="tabpanel" class="feature-content fade tab-feature-content panel-body fw-previous-tab-pane active in" id="wordpress-which-package">
<p>For newer WordPress sites, we definitely recommend our high speed Shared Hosting solutions. These solutions are <strong>high speed and easy-to-use</strong>. They are the perfect springboard to get your site up and running. Once your site grows, or if you have an existing site, you may want to consider one of our Managed VPS plans. Our Managed VPS plans offer the same ease of use as our Shared Hosting, you'll get <strong>more power and support</strong> from them. The good news is that at A2 Hosting, our hosting plans are completely scalable and can grow as your site grows. That means you don't have to worry about outgrowing your solution. We have a full lineup of services that we can seamlessly move your site into.</p>
<p>We encourage you to contact our sales team if you have any questions about our hosting packages and which one will best fit your site.</p>
